This Ice Fly watch has a deep blue silicone strap and a colourful dial which features a bird print in orange and tones of blue. The birds range in colour, size and style and from a distance give the appearance of camouflage. The dial measures approximately 43mm in width, including the winder, so it is suitable for both men and women. Gold coloured hands stand out on the dial against the patterned background and other gold coloured details such as the crown and the buckle tie the design together. The Ice logo features on the strap retainer as well as on the dial adjacent to the crown. This watch is supplied in the correct, official branded presentation box and is accompanied by a two year manufacturer’s warranty.
